Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.11,0:24:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\an5\fs30\shad0\bord2\3c&H030407&\pos(320,250)}撕開黑暗的車頭燈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.78,0:24:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\an5\fs30\shad0\bord2\3c&H030407&\pos(320,250)}「可選各種顏色」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.24,0:24:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\an5\fs30\shad0\bord2\3c&H030407&\pos(320,250)\fad(300,0)}戴上頭盔吧！
